<!-- Alur & Langkah Pendaftaran -->
<section id="langkah" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 scroll-mt-20 w-full">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-xs font-bold text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 tracking-widest uppercase bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-950/40 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-teal-100 dark:border-teal-900/60">Bagaimana Cara Bergabung?</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 dark:text-white tracking-tight mt-4">Alur Pendaftaran Magang</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-3 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base">Ikuti 4 langkah mudah berikut untuk memulai perjalanan karir magang Anda bersama Pemkot Banjarmasin.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative w-full">
        <!-- Line Connector Desktop -->
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-[40px] left-[12%] right-[12%] h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-200 via-emerald-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-teal-900 dark:via-emerald-950 dark:to-gray-800 -z-10"></div>
        <!-- Line Connector Mobile -->
        <div class="block md:hidden absolute left-[35px] top-[40px] bottom-[40px] w-[2px] bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-200 via-emerald-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-teal-900 dark:via-emerald-950 dark:to-gray-800 -z-10"></div>

        <!-- Langkah 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-layout flex flex-row md:flex-col items-start md:items-center text-left md:text-center gap-5 w-full group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-950/40 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl shadow-inner border border-teal-100/50 dark:border-teal-900/50 relative shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <i class="fas fa-user-plus text-base"></i>
                <span class="absolute -top-1.5 -right-1.5 w-5 h-5 bg-teal-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-800"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white text-lg mb-2">1. Buat Akun</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed">Registrasikan data diri Anda pada portal dengan email aktif & isi profil akademis lengkap.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Langkah 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-layout flex flex-row md:flex-col items-start md:items-center text-left md:text-center gap-5 w-full group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-950/40 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl shadow-inner border border-teal-100/50 dark:border-teal-900/50 relative shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <i class="fas fa-search-location text-base"></i>
                <span class="absolute -top-1.5 -right-1.5 w-5 h-5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-355 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-800">2</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white text-lg mb-2">2. Pilih Lowongan</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed">Cari dinas instansi yang relevan dengan kualifikasi jurusan dan minat karir Anda.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Langkah 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-layout flex flex-row md:flex-col items-start md:items-center text-left md:text-center gap-5 w-full group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-950/40 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl shadow-inner border border-teal-100/50 dark:border-teal-900/50 relative shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt text-base"></i>
                <span class="absolute -top-1.5 -right-1.5 w-5 h-5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-355 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-800">3</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white text-lg mb-2">3. Slot Periode</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed">Tentukan tanggal masuk & selesai. Sistem akan memvalidasi sisa kuota yang tersedia.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Langkah 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700/50 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-layout flex flex-row md:flex-col items-start md:items-center text-left md:text-center gap-5 w-full group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-950/40 text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-xl shadow-inner border border-teal-100/50 dark:border-teal-900/50 relative shrink-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane text-base"></i>
                <span class="absolute -top-1.5 -right-1.5 w-5 h-5 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-355 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white dark:border-slate-800">4</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white text-lg mb-2">4. Mulai Magang</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed">Setelah divalidasi oleh instansi tujuan, Anda siap diterjunkan & mendapatkan pembimbing.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
